title: Purchasing land in Sandbox
body:
Much like Decentraland, Sandbox is massive currently for those wishing to build foundations within the Metaverse. It would be beneficial to buy land in Sandbox for future Mutantverse activities. Specifics of land purchase to be discussed if this vote passes.
Do you approve of using DAO funds to buy land in Sandbox upon discussing specifics as a community?
author: 0xa11435b21e0Eff08A6c2c5b8316ACC94054e8bAB
